org.eclipse.papyrus.MARTE.MARTE_Foundations.NFPs

Interface NfpType

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, TupleType
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    NfpTypeImpl

    public interface NfpType
extends TupleType
    A representation of the model object 'Nfp Type'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Value Attrib
    • Unit Attrib
    • Expr Attrib
    See Also:
    NFPsPackage.getNfpType()
